headline.main: Tyron Woodley Chooses Smarts Over Slugfest, Keeps UFC Belt
headline.print_headline: Tyron Woodley Chooses Smarts Over Slugfest, Keeps UFC Belt

lead_paragraph: Tyron Woodley understood the booing that thoroughly drowned out his words when he spoke to the fans following his tactical victory over Stephen Thompson at UFC 209.
